Vous comptez les vendre ?

157
00:09:45,170 --> 00:09:46,771
<font color="#ffff33">- Oh yeah, we will. - Mm-hmm.</font>
Oui.

158
00:09:46,791 --> 00:09:48,790
<font color="#ffff33">All right.</font>
Super.

159
00:09:49,500 --> 00:09:52,416
<font color="#ffff33">So you guys are what? Like, a cult?</font>
Vous êtes quoi ? Une secte ?

160
00:09:53,380 --> 00:09:58,360
<font color="#ffff33">We are idealistic individuals who want to build a better world.</font>
Juste des idéalistes qui veulent construire un monde meilleur.

161
00:09:58,380 --> 00:10:00,750
<font color="#ffff33">Yeah, that's a cult.</font>
Ouais, une secte, quoi.

162
00:10:00,833 --> 00:10:04,360
<font color="#ffff33">- What? - It's all right, not judging.</font>
- Pardon ? - C'est bon, je juge pas.

163
00:10:04,380 --> 00:10:06,830
<font color="#ffff33">Just pay me. We're good.</font>
Payez-moi, c'est tout.

164
00:10:10,083 --> 00:10:14,150
<font color="#ffff33">Hey guys, you should, uh... you should see this.</font>
Hé, vous devriez venir voir ça.

165
00:10:14,170 --> 00:10:19,313
<font color="#ffff33">What? - Oh... - Oh shit.</font>
- Quoi ? - Oh, merde.

166
00:10:19,333 --> 00:10:21,210
<font color="#ffff33">What?</font>
Quoi ?

167
00:10:22,541 --> 00:10:24,063
<font color="#ffff33">Are you serious?</font>
Sérieux ?

168
00:10:24,083 --> 00:10:26,563
<font color="#ffff33">- Newsflash, we're in deep Texas. - I don't care.</font>
- Scoop, on est au Texas. - Je m'en fiche.

169
00:10:26,583 --> 00:10:29,110
<font color="#ffff33">We have a bus full of potential investors on the way.</font>
On attend un bus rempli d'investisseurs.

170
00:10:29,130 --> 00:10:30,980
<font color="#ffff33">They see this flag, they're not gonna buy.</font>
Avec ce drapeau, c'est foutu.

171
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:32,610
<font color="#ffff33">- Trust me. - I'm getting the cowboy.</font>
Je vais chercher ce type.

172
00:10:32,630 --> 00:10:34,790
<font color="#ffff33">Mel, help me.</font>
Mel, aide-moi.

173
00:10:35,210 --> 00:10:37,360
<font color="#ffff33">I'll just be here.</font>
Je vous attends là.

174
00:10:37,380 --> 00:10:42,730
<font color="#ffff33"></font>
ORPHELINAT DE HARLOW DEPUIS 1925

175
00:10:42,750 --> 00:10:45,750
<font color="#ffff33">Hmm...</font>


176
00:10:47,170 --> 00:10:49,400
<font color="#ffff33">Um, I'm going upstairs.</font>
Je monte.

177
00:10:49,420 --> 00:10:53,333
<font color="#ffff33">Look at this place. It's weird.</font>
Regarde-moi cet endroit. Trop bizarre.

178
00:11:07,210 --> 00:11:09,708
<font color="#ffff33">Ah, shit.</font>
Putain.

179
00:11:18,040 --> 00:11:21,920
<font color="#ffff33"></font>
ORPHELINAT DE HARLOW, 1975

180
00:11:25,670 --> 00:11:28,521
<font color="#ffff33">Damn, I couldn't reach it.</font>
J'ai pas réussi à l'atteindre.

181
00:11:28,541 --> 00:11:32,190
<font color="#ffff33">- Oh shit. Well, what are we going to do? - Let's just wait for the contractor.</font>
- Merde, on fait quoi ? - Attendons l'entrepreneur.

182
00:11:32,210 --> 00:11:34,875
<font color="#ffff33">What are you doing in our house?</font>
Que faites-vous chez nous ?

183
00:11:36,130 --> 00:11:37,900
<font color="#ffff33">Uh, I'm sorry. I didn't realize...</font>
Désolé. Je ne savais pas…

184
00:11:37,920 --> 00:11:40,830
<font color="#ffff33">We thought this place was empty.</font>
On croyait que c'était inhabité.

185
00:11:50,083 --> 00:11:54,125
<font color="#ffff33">Oh, you're the new neighbors, aren't you?</font>
Vous êtes les nouveaux voisins, non ?

186
00:11:54,250 --> 00:11:56,333
<font color="#ffff33">Uh...</font>


187
00:11:56,710 --> 00:11:59,190
<font color="#ffff33">Wish I'd known y'all were coming.</font>
Vous auriez dû me prévenir.

188
00:11:59,210 --> 00:12:01,875
<font color="#ffff33">I'd have put my face on.</font>
Je me serais faite belle.

189
00:12:07,291 --> 00:12:09,416
<font color="#ffff33">Sweet tea?</font>
Un thé glacé ?

190
00:12:12,833 --> 00:12:16,440
<font color="#ffff33">I've been running this orphanage for nearly 50 years.</font>
J'ai dirigé cet orphelinat pendant presque 50 ans.

191
00:12:16,460 --> 00:12:20,650
<font color="#ffff33">I've housed boys and girls in need of a loving home,</font>
J'ai hébergé des garçons et des filles en quête d'un foyer,

192
00:12:20,670 --> 00:12:27,480
<font color="#ffff33">and troubled teens that needed me to show 'em mercy for their ways.</font>
des adolescents perturbés qui avaient besoin de ma compassion.

193
00:12:27,500 --> 00:12:28,440
<font color="#ffff33">Please.</font>
Buvez.

194
00:12:28,460 --> 00:12:34,690
<font color="#ffff33">Ma'am, the bank, um, reclaimed this property months ago.</font>
Madame, la banque a récupéré cette propriété il y a des mois.

195
00:12:34,710 --> 00:12:37,375
<font color="#ffff33">You're not supposed to be here.</font>
Ce n'est plus chez vous.

196
00:12:39,583 --> 00:12:43,313
<font color="#ffff33">You talking about that whole mix up with the bank?</font>
Vous voulez parler de ce quiproquo avec la banque ?

197
00:12:43,333 --> 00:12:45,900
<font color="#ffff33">That's been settled.</font>
C'est réglé.

198
00:12:45,920 --> 00:12:49,650
<font color="#ffff33">I paid everything I owed. This is still our house.</font>
J'ai payé tout ce que je devais. C'est toujours notre maison.

199
00:12:49,670 --> 00:12:51,771
<font color="#ffff33">You're wrong. I'm sorry, but...</font>
C'est faux. Navré, mais…

200
00:12:51,791 --> 00:12:54,150
<font color="#ffff33">I've got a title that says otherwise.</font>
J'ai un document qui dit le contraire.

201
00:12:54,170 --> 00:12:56,790
<font color="#ffff33">Do you mind if we see that?</font>
Vous nous le montrez ?

202
00:12:58,130 --> 00:12:59,730
<font color="#ffff33">I don't have to show you anything.</font>
Je n'y suis pas obligée.

203
00:12:59,750 --> 00:13:03,880
<font color="#ffff33">- That's because you don't have it. - Dante, don't.</font>
- Donc, vous ne l'avez pas. - Arrête.

204
00:13:04,710 --> 00:13:08,416
<font color="#ffff33">What? Was this about my flag?</font>
Quoi ? C'est à cause de mon drapeau ?

205
00:13:09,791 --> 00:13:12,271
<font color="#ffff33">You got me all wrong.</font>
Vous vous méprenez.

206
00:13:12,291 --> 00:13:16,813
<font color="#ffff33">I've taken care of many boys like you over the years.</font>
J'ai accueilli beaucoup de garçons comme vous au fil des années.

207
00:13:16,833 --> 00:13:20,208
<font color="#ffff33">I don't have a problem with Negroes.</font>
Je n'ai rien contre votre espèce.

208
00:13:21,210 --> 00:13:22,771
<font color="#ffff33">Okay. Fuck this.</font>
OK. Je vous emmerde.

209
00:13:22,791 --> 00:13:24,610
<font color="#ffff33">You watch your mouth, boy.</font>
Votre langage, jeune homme.

210
00:13:24,630 --> 00:13:26,190
<font color="#ffff33">You watch yours.</font>
Le vôtre d'abord.

211
00:13:26,210 --> 00:13:27,440
<font color="#ffff33">Where are you going?</font>
Tu vas où ?

212
00:13:27,460 --> 00:13:30,440
<font color="#ffff33">Let the cops deal with her. I don't have time for this.</font>
Les flics géreront. Pas le temps pour ça.

213
00:13:30,460 --> 00:13:32,708
<font color="#ffff33">I'm getting the sheriff.</font>
J'appelle le shérif.

214
00:13:34,041 --> 00:13:36,458
<font color="#ffff33">It's not what you think.</font>
Vous vous trompez.

215
00:13:36,500 --> 00:13:40,563
<font color="#ffff33">That flag belonged to my great granddaddy.</font>
Ce drapeau appartenait à mon arrière-grand-père.

216
00:13:40,583 --> 00:13:44,458
<font color="#ffff33">It reminds me of him.</font>
Ça me fait penser à lui.

217
00:13:44,750 --> 00:13:48,375
<font color="#ffff33">I haven't given it much thought.</font>
Je n'y ai pas vraiment réfléchi.

218
00:13:48,880 --> 00:13:52,875
<font color="#ffff33">I... I understand your friend.</font>
Je comprends votre ami.

219
00:13:54,791 --> 00:13:57,690
<font color="#ffff33">I wish I could help you, but you can't be here.</font>
J'aimerais vous aider, mais ce n'est plus chez vous.

220
00:13:57,710 --> 00:14:00,690
<font color="#ffff33">There are shelters for the elderly, and...</font>
Il y a des foyers pour personnes âgées et…

221
00:14:00,710 --> 00:14:04,771
<font color="#ffff33">Shelter? I'm not going anywhere.</font>
Un foyer ? Je n'irai nulle part.

222
00:14:04,791 --> 00:14:08,110
<font color="#ffff33">I told you. This is our house.</font>
Je vous l'ai dit. C'est notre maison.

223
00:14:08,130 --> 00:14:11,110
<font color="#ffff33">Look, you'll be safer in a home and better taken care of.</font>
Vous y serez en sécurité, on prendra soin de vous.

224
00:14:11,130 --> 00:14:14,375
<font color="#ffff33">A woman your age shouldn't be on her own.</font>
À votre âge, on ne reste pas seule.

225
00:14:17,460 --> 00:14:21,730
<font color="#ffff33">Baby, I'm fine. I'm all right.</font>
Mon chéri, c'est rien. Je vais bien.

226
00:14:21,750 --> 00:14:25,125
<font color="#ffff33">Just go back to your room.</font>
Retourne dans ta chambre.

227
00:14:25,920 --> 00:14:29,375
<font color="#ffff33">He's the last of my boys.</font>
C'est le dernier de mes garçons.

228
00:14:29,460 --> 00:14:30,730
<font color="#ffff33">He needs special care.</font>
Il est spécial.

229
00:14:30,750 --> 00:14:32,940
<font color="#ffff33">He doesn't do well outside, you understand that?</font>
Dehors, il est inadapté, compris ?

230
00:14:32,960 --> 00:14:35,750
<font color="#ffff33">It's why I can't ever leave here.</font>
Je ne peux donc pas partir.

231
00:14:38,500 --> 00:14:41,250
<font color="#ffff33">Christ, Ginny, why are you still here?</font>
Ginny, t'es encore là ?

232
00:14:41,630 --> 00:14:43,313
<font color="#ffff33">What have you done?</font>
Qu'avez-vous fait ?

233
00:14:43,333 --> 00:14:44,980
<font color="#ffff33">Virginia, we told you weeks ago.</font>
Virginia, tu le savais.

234
00:14:45,000 --> 00:14:47,021
<font color="#ffff33">She ain't listening. Let's get her outta here.</font>
Elle n'écoute pas. Sortons-la d'ici.

235
00:14:47,041 --> 00:14:50,610
<font color="#ffff33">- We'll talk about it outside. - Come on. Let's go.</font>
- On en parlera dehors. - Allez.

236
00:14:50,630 --> 00:14:51,730
<font color="#ffff33">Take it easy.</font>
Doucement.

237
00:14:51,750 --> 00:14:53,958
<font color="#ffff33">I barely touched her.</font>
Je l'ai pas touchée.

238
00:14:53,960 --> 00:14:57,860
<font color="#ffff33">Oh my God. What is happening? We need to call an ambulance.</font>
Mon Dieu ! Que se passe-t-il ? Il faut appeler une ambulance.

239
00:14:57,880 --> 00:14:59,400
<font color="#ffff33">We are the ambulance.</font>
C'est nous, l'ambulance.

240
00:14:59,420 --> 00:15:02,208
<font color="#ffff33">It's all right. It's her boy.</font>
Pas de souci. C'est son fils.

241
00:15:02,420 --> 00:15:05,190
<font color="#ffff33">Grab the oxygen. Put her in the van.</font>
Prends l'oxygène. Mets-la dans le fourgon.

242
00:15:05,210 --> 00:15:08,080
<font color="#ffff33">She's having a heart attack.</font>
Elle fait une crise cardiaque.

243
00:15:08,291 --> 00:15:10,360
<font color="#ffff33">The check... It was... Please...</font>
Le chèque… c'était… pitié…

244
00:15:10,380 --> 00:15:11,688
<font color="#ffff33">Hey, hey, what did you do?</font>
Il se passe quoi ?

245
00:15:11,708 --> 00:15:14,400
<font color="#ffff33">We'll get you to the hospital in no time. Just hold on.</font>
On t'emmène à l'hôpital. Tiens bon.

246
00:15:14,420 --> 00:15:17,021
<font color="#ffff33">Shit. The bus is here.</font>
Merde. Le bus est là.

247
00:15:17,041 --> 00:15:18,521
<font color="#ffff33">Fuck.</font>
Putain.

248
00:15:18,541 --> 00:15:19,813
<font color="#ffff33">I'm going with her.</font>
Je l'accompagne.

249
00:15:19,833 --> 00:15:22,480
<font color="#ffff33">No, Melody, no, no, no. I'll go with her. I'll go.</font>
Non, Melody. Je l'accompagne.

250
00:15:22,500 --> 00:15:23,440
<font color="#ffff33">What?</font>
Quoi ?

251
00:15:23,460 --> 00:15:25,440
<font color="#ffff33">Everyone's expecting to see the two of you.</font>
Ils viennent pour vous deux.

252
00:15:25,460 --> 00:15:26,400
<font color="#ffff33">She'll be okay.</font>
Elle ira bien.

253
00:15:26,420 --> 00:15:27,980
<font color="#ffff33">Come on.</font>
Allez.

254
00:15:28,000 --> 00:15:29,730
<font color="#ffff33">- Christ. - Somebody needs to.</font>
Bon sang.

255
00:15:29,750 --> 00:15:31,440
<font color="#ffff33">It can't be Melody, can't be you.</font>
Quelqu'un doit y aller. Ni Melody ni toi.

256
00:15:31,460 --> 00:15:35,440
<font color="#ffff33">You need to focus on this. I'll be back as soon as I can.</font>
Reste concentré. Je reviendrai vite.

257
00:15:35,460 --> 00:15:38,480
<font color="#ffff33">Okay. Please just make sure she's all right.</font>
OK. Assure-toi qu'elle s'en sorte.

258
00:15:38,500 --> 00:15:40,190
<font color="#ffff33">Thank you. You're an angel.</font>
Merci. T'es un ange.

259
00:15:40,210 --> 00:15:42,210
<font color="#ffff33">Let's move.</font>
On y va.

260
00:15:55,541 --> 00:15:57,958
<font color="#ffff33">Here's your flag.</font>
Voilà votre drapeau.

261
00:16:02,541 --> 00:16:07,208
<font color="#ffff33">Come on, Mel. We'll get somebody to clean that up.</font>
Viens. On trouvera quelqu'un pour nettoyer.

262
00:16:08,710 --> 00:16:10,813
<font color="#ffff33">Did that not feel like a bad omen to you?</font>
C'est pas un mauvais présage ?

263
00:16:10,833 --> 00:16:12,110
<font color="#ffff33">This place is cursed now.</font>
C'est maudit, ici.

264
00:16:12,130 --> 00:16:13,900
<font color="#ffff33">Please, this is not...</font>
Je t'en prie, arrête…

265
00:16:13,920 --> 00:16:16,360
<font color="#ffff33">I don't need this right now, so... it's all good.</font>
C'est pas le moment.

266
00:16:16,380 --> 00:16:20,146
<font color="#ffff33">If you move here, I'm moving back with Dad.</font>
Je te jure, je rentre chez papa.

267
00:16:20,166 --> 00:16:22,063
<font color="#ffff33">No, you're not.</font>
Non.

268
00:16:22,083 --> 00:16:24,730
<font color="#ffff33">I... I don't want to live here. Your whole idea is insane.</font>
Je veux pas vivre ici. C'est ridicule.

269
00:16:24,750 --> 00:16:29,020
<font color="#ffff33">- You don't know what you want. - Okay, and you do?</font>
- Tu ne sais pas ce que tu veux. - OK, et toi ?

270
00:16:29,040 --> 00:16:33,521
<font color="#ffff33">Uh, I know you need me, and you can't take care of yourself.</font>
Je sais que t'as besoin que je m'occupe de toi.

271
00:16:33,541 --> 00:16:35,540
<font color="#ffff33">Wait.</font>
Attends.

272
00:16:36,960 --> 00:16:39,000
<font color="#ffff33">Why did I...?</font>
Bon sang…

273
00:16:39,380 --> 00:16:41,940
<font color="#ffff33">Honestly, the bank could've never dreamed of selling these</font>
La banque n'aurait jamais pu vendre tout ça

274
00:16:41,960 --> 00:16:43,230
<font color="#ffff33">without your help, Dante.</font>
sans vous, Dante.

275
00:16:43,250 --> 00:16:45,230
<font color="#ffff33">- Thank you for trusting us. - It's amazing.</font>
- Merci d'y avoir cru. - Génial.

276
00:16:45,250 --> 00:16:46,610
<font color="#ffff33">Absolutely. Um...</font>
C'est vrai.

277
00:16:46,630 --> 00:16:49,650
<font color="#ffff33">Mel! Mel! Catherine, come here.</font>
Mel ! Catherine, par ici.

278
00:16:49,670 --> 00:16:52,060
<font color="#ffff33">This is Catherine, you know, from the bank. She made all this possible.</font>
Voici Catherine, de la banque.

279
00:16:52,080 --> 00:16:53,771
<font color="#ffff33"></font>
On lui doit tout.

280
00:16:53,791 --> 00:16:56,830
<font color="#ffff33">Finally. It's nice to meet you.</font>
Enfin ! Ravie de vous rencontrer.

281
00:16:57,210 --> 00:17:01,150
<font color="#ffff33">You know, everyone is super excited. You guys did a great job promoting this.</font>
On est tous super impatients. Vous avez fait une belle promo.

282
00:17:01,170 --> 00:17:03,021
<font color="#ffff33">Yeah, just needs a fresh coat of paint.</font>
Il manque un coup de peinture.

283
00:17:03,041 --> 00:17:05,190
<font color="#ffff33">Oh no, it is perfect like this.</font>
Oh non, c'est parfait comme ça.

284
00:17:05,210 --> 00:17:07,771
<font color="#ffff33">These people want the wear-down. You know, the history?</font>
Ils aiment l'ancien. Vous voyez, le vécu ?

285
00:17:07,791 --> 00:17:08,900
<font color="#ffff33">Yeah. Absolutely. Yeah.</font>
Oui. Absolument.

286
00:17:08,920 --> 00:17:10,900
<font color="#ffff33">- This is going to be great. - Yeah.</font>
- Ça va être génial. - Oui.

287
00:17:10,920 --> 00:17:15,271
<font color="#ffff33">I'm just going to start setting up, so... Okay.</font>
Je dois commencer à tout installer, alors…

288
00:17:15,291 --> 00:17:16,271
<font color="#ffff33">Is she all right?</font>
Elle va bien ?

289
00:17:16,291 --> 00:17:18,521
<font color="#ffff33">Yeah, I think the heat's just getting to her a bit.</font>
Oui, juste un petit coup de chaleur.

290
00:17:18,541 --> 00:17:19,563
<font color="#ffff33">It's so hot out here.</font>
On crève, ici.

291
00:17:19,583 --> 00:17:23,750
<font color="#ffff33">- Probably needed a little water. - Yeah. It's hot.</font>
- Déshydratation. - Oui. Il fait chaud.

292
00:17:28,750 --> 00:17:31,000
<font color="#ffff33">How's she doing?</font>
Comment va-t-elle ?

293
00:17:34,170 --> 00:17:41,110
<font color="#ffff33">Baby, who's the good boy I taught you to be?</font>
Mon chéri, c'est qui le gentil petit garçon ?

294
00:17:41,130 --> 00:17:44,125
<font color="#ffff33">Stay out of my room.</font>
N'entre pas dans ma chambre.

295
00:18:01,250 --> 00:18:03,250
<font color="#ffff33">Shit.</font>
Merde.

296
00:18:03,420 --> 00:18:05,400
<font color="#ffff33">Sheriff, I think she croaked.</font>
Shérif, elle a clamsé, je crois.

297
00:18:05,420 --> 00:18:08,040
<font color="#ffff33">Son of a bitch.</font>
Bordel.

298
00:18:09,041 --> 00:18:11,170
<font color="#ffff33">Oh my God.</font>
Oh, mon Dieu !

299
00:18:26,666 --> 00:18:28,666
<font color="#ffff33">Hey.</font>


300
00:18:37,250 --> 00:18:39,250
<font color="#ffff33">No!</font>
Non !

301
00:18:47,333 --> 00:18:49,625
<font color="#ffff33">What the hell's going on?</font>
C'était quoi, ça ?

302
00:18:54,670 --> 00:18:56,830
<font color="#ffff33">Oh my God!</font>
Oh, mon Dieu !

303
00:19:06,130 --> 00:19:08,480
<font color="#ffff33">And sold to Candace Brady of Brady's Brunch.</font>
Vendu à Candace, de Brady's Brunch.

304
00:19:08,500 --> 00:19:11,625
<font color="#ffff33">Aw! I love brunch. That's great.</font>
Oh ! J'adore le brunch. Génial.

305
00:19:12,380 --> 00:19:14,271
<font color="#ffff33">Well, this was built in 1910,</font>
Elle a été construite en 1910,

306
00:19:14,291 --> 00:19:20,166
<font color="#ffff33">and once counted President Howard Taft as a distinguished guest.</font>
et le président Howard Taft y a même résidé.

307
00:19:23,500 --> 00:19:26,980
<font color="#ffff33">Got a high chance of thunderstorms, lightning, and heavy rain.</font>
On s'attend à des orages, des éclairs et des averses.

308
00:19:27,000 --> 00:19:29,210
<font color="#ffff33">Stay dry out there.</font>
Restez bien au sec.

309
00:19:30,880 --> 00:19:34,271
<font color="#ffff33">So, Richter...</font>
Alors, Richter…

310
00:19:34,291 --> 00:19:36,480
<font color="#ffff33">why are you such a nihilist?</font>
pourquoi être si nihiliste ?

